headline: Is ONEOK A Bargain After Recent Share Price Slide And DCF Upside In 2025?
summary: If you are wondering whether ONEOK is a bargain or a value trap at today’s price, you are not alone. This piece walks through what the numbers actually say about it. The stock has bounced about 3.3% over the last week and 4.2% over the past month, but it is still down roughly 27.8% year to date and 24.3% over the last year. This is despite being up 30.1% over 3 years and 157.8% over 5 years. Recent moves have been driven by shifting expectations around US natural gas and NGL demand,...
